## 📋 **Executive Summary**

This instruction map provides comprehensive guidance for **structuring and fine-tuning the 10 enhanced strategies** implemented in the StatArb_Gemini core_engine with **dynamic parameter adaptation to market conditions**. The workflow follows **"Escort Development"** engineering practice with full **13-rules compliance** and institutional-grade standards.

## 🎯 **Core Objective: Strategy Fine-Tuning & Dynamic Adaptation**

**Primary Goal**: Structure and fine-tune the 10 strategies in core_engine with market-adaptive parameter optimization
